# Skill Registry

根据用户意图匹配对应 Skill，读取其 SKILL.md 执行。路径相对于项目根目录。

## 开发效率（11）

| 触发意图 | Skill | 路径 |
|---------|-------|------|
| 提交代码、commit | git-commit-standard | `generated-skills/git-commit-standard/` |
| 审查代码、review | code-review-assistant | `generated-skills/code-review-assistant/` |
| 写测试、补测试 | test-generator | `generated-skills/test-generator/` |
| 报错、调试 | error-diagnostics | `generated-skills/error-diagnostics/` |
| 查 API、查文档 | api-doc-lookup | `generated-skills/api-doc-lookup/` |
| SQL、数据库 | sql-assistant | `generated-skills/sql-assistant/` |
| 重构、拆函数 | refactor-helper | `generated-skills/refactor-helper/` |
| 生成文档、README | doc-generator | `generated-skills/doc-generator/` |
| Docker、CI/CD、配置 | env-config-template | `generated-skills/env-config-template/` |
| 国际化、多语言 | i18n-helper | `generated-skills/i18n-helper/` |
| 循环重试、做到通过 | auto-retry-loop | `generated-skills/auto-retry-loop/` |

